title: and Megan Fox and Machine Gun Kelly
description:
Famed Astrologist Susan Miller of Astrology Zone reads charts for Lala, Randall, Megan Fox and Machine Gun Kelly, and answers all of their burning questions about love, marriage, babies, and money! Plus, Megan and MGK share their love story that started with an instant connection in Puerto Rico on the set of Randall’s movie, “Midnight In the Switchgrass.”

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
